		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">List of Boston Legal episodes</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>The following is a list of the episodes of the <a href="/wiki/Television_series" title="Television series" class="mw-redirect">television series</a> <i><b><a href="/wiki/Boston_Legal" title="Boston Legal">Boston Legal</a></b></i>. The series premiered on <a href="/wiki/American_Broadcasting_Company" title="American Broadcasting Company">ABC</a> on October 3, 2004 in the United States, and ended on December 8, 2008, bringing the episode total to 101.</p>
