<td class="description" style="border-bottom:3px solid #008080" colspan="6">Denny is arrested on concealed-weapon charges after shooting a man who tried to mug him and Jerry. Sack and Jerry defend him, but Sack is put off by Jerry and Crane's alternate agenda for the case. When Alan represents Joanna, a sexual surrogate, in a custody battle for her daughter, he tries to come to terms with the accusation that he's sexist.&#160;</td>
</tr>
<tr class="vevent" style="text-align: center; background:#F2F2F2">
