<td>Steve Robin</td>
<td>2008-10-13</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="description" style="border-bottom:3px solid #008080" colspan="6">When Pheobe hires Alan to help her husband beat a murder charge, he faces a moral and professional dilemma when his lingering feelings for her elicit a secret desire for a conviction.&#160;</td>
</tr>
<tr class="vevent" style="text-align: center; background:#F2F2F2">
<td id="ep93">93</td>
