<tr>
<td class="description" style="border-bottom:3px solid #008080" colspan="6">Alan and Shirley prepare for an uphill fight with the military on behalf of a man whose brother died in a military hospital under suspicious circumstances. Meanwhile, Jerry helps his sister Joy (<a href="/wiki/Annie_Potts" title="Annie Potts">Annie Potts</a>) in her search for the identity of the father of her son.&#160;</td>
</tr>
<tr class="vevent" style="text-align: center; background:#F2F2F2">
<td id="ep94">94</td>
