<tr>
<td class="description" style="border-bottom:3px solid #008080" colspan="6">Denny and Alan visit a Dude Ranch in Utah, but find themselves in trouble with their tour group and the local authorities, including Melvin Palmer. Back in Boston, Shirley defends Catherine Piper after she unintentionally blows up her doctor when she sets his office on fire in revenge for prescribing her drugs that gave her a heart attack.&#160;</td>
</tr>
<tr class="vevent" style="text-align: center; background:#F2F2F2">
