</tr>
<tr>
<td class="description" style="border-bottom:3px solid #008080" colspan="6">Alan goes up against Denise Bauer and the USDA when he represents a cattle rancher, Carol Hober (<a href="/wiki/Valerie_Bertinelli" title="Valerie Bertinelli">Valerie Bertinelli</a>) who is suing the government for not allowing her to test all her livestock for Mad Cow Disease. Crane quickly irritates Hober by insisting that she looks like and is Valerie Bertinelli. Meanwhile, Jerry is up for partner but the panel of partners deciding his fate, including Paul Lewiston, see his social inadequacies as a problem.&#160;</td>
</tr>
<tr class="vevent" style="text-align: center; background:#F2F2F2">
